definitions.dict_definition:
@rằn
- (địa phương) Striped
=Vải rằn+Striped cloth

@rằn ri
- Striped, checquered
=Khăn rằn ri+A checquered scarf, a checquered headkerchief

@rằm
- The fifteenth of the lunar month, the full-moon day
=Trăng rằm+The moon on the night of the fifteenth of the lunar month, a full moon
